Malaysia’s Anwar Lodges Police Report on Sex Video, Star Says

-- B y   B a r r y   P o r t e r
-- 
2011-03-22T07:48:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-22/malaysia-s-anwar-lodges-police-report-on-sex-video-star-says.html
Anwar Ibrahim,  Malaysia ’s
opposition leader, lodged a police report today following the
release of a sex video allegedly implicating an unidentified
senior opposition politician, the Star reported on its website.  Anwar denied he was the man on the tape in the police
report, the newspaper said. The video was shown to a select
group of journalists yesterday, it said.    To contact the editor responsible for this story:
